# GitHub template note:
# Task commands are backed by the repository pointed to by the local `upstream`
# remote. The task tools require the GitHub CLI (`gh`) authenticated with
# `gh auth login`; agents should still use bin/task-* for task state.
#
# If agentws/server.url exists, job commands use that remote AgentWS job server
# and mirror claimed jobs under agentws/jobs/. Without server.url, jobs are
# stored locally under agentws/jobs/.
#
# AgentWS-owned issue labels are prefixed with the authenticated GitHub login:
#   gh api user --jq .login
# producing:
#   <login>-agentws-running
#   <login>-agentws-done
